module.exports = "<div class=\"parallax featured-services-img\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 parallax-heading-container\">\n                <h1 class=\"lg-text\">CARDIAC TREATMENT</h1>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"container paddingTB60\">\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        India is emerging as one of the pioneer hub for medical tourism. Over the years, with renowned hospitals and research centres being established, the increase in the number of highly-qualified doctors and their specialties, and not to forget the affordable\n        treatment costs, as compared to places like the USA or the Europe, India is one the brink of becoming a global medical hub.\n    </p>\n    <br>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Numerous numbers of patients pour in each day for several medical treatments, but the majority of them come to India for heart treatments. Not only international patient, but people from different corners of the country prefer to get their heart treated\n        in India. It is estimated that in India, almost one lac bye pass heart surgeries are conducted in a year. Let alone a bypass surgery, doctors in India, with their 98% success rate in the operation theaters, are so skillful and their first hand\n        experience combined, allows them to take up surgeries like angioplasty, valve replacement, open heart surgeries invasive heart surgery or any other kind of treatment.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Heart treatment is a very complex and complicated process that requires advanced medical equipments, expensive drugs and highly trained professionals and to top all these, heart treatments are a costly process. But, in India, the cost of a heart surgery\n        isnâ€™t that expensive. Even though the standard of quality is maintained at par with the finest hospitals around the world, the operation of a heart bypass surgery is lower than other western countries by a margin of at least 60-70 percent. This\n        is the main reason that draws international heart patients looking for bypass and angioplasty to India.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Given the complexity of heart treatments, the institutions and the hospitals are now equipped with high end technology and tools to perform these complex surgeries.\n    </p>\n</div>"

