module.exports = "<div class=\"parallax featured-services-img\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 parallax-heading-container\">\n                <h1 class=\"lg-text\">\n                    COSMETIC & PLASTIC SURGERY\n                </h1>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"container paddingTB60\">\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Cosmetic Surgery or Aesthetic surgery helps to modify or improve the appearance of a physical feature, irregularity, or defect. Cosmetic Surgery can make changes on the functioning parts of your body in order to make that part to look better. Cosmetic\n        surgery is a form of Plastic surgery. Plastic Surgery is a broader field of surgery primarily concerned with moulding or moving tissues for healing, improving function or to correct the congenital defects or those acquired later by trauma or surgery.\n        Cosmetic surgery can be performed on all areas of the head, neck and body. Because treated areas function properly but lack aesthetic appeal, cosmetic surgery is elective. Cosmetic surgery is one of the fast evolving branches of medicine with\n        newer methods, technique and technology coming into this field.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Many people travel around the world in search of affordable and high quality cosmetic surgery. One of the most favourite cosmetic surgery destinations among medical travellers is India. There are many Cosmetic Surgery centres in India that offer world-class\n        cosmetic surgery at unbelievably low cost.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        At MediAide, we have picked some of the best cosmetic surgery centres in India to form a wide network and to give you best options for your cosmetic surgery.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Our network cosmetic surgery centres in India offer various cosmetic treatments and surgeries backed by an internationally trained team of surgeons and dermatologists with vast experience in this field. Some of the centres even have board certified cosmetic\n        surgeons who have a vast experience in this field. The plastic surgeons have the expertise in doing complex micro vascular surgery or reconstructive microsurgery where the surgeries are done using an operating microscope to cut and join tiny blood\n        vessels and nerves, most between half a millimetre and 2 millimetres in size. Our network centres are equipped with cutting edge microsurgical equipment. The surgeons have performed complicated cases of replantation or re-attachment of amputated\n        body parts like fingers, hands, limbs etc. They also have expertise in cancer reconstruction using micro vascular tissue transfer, immediate reconstruction of major limb injuries, reconstruction of missing fingers or thumbs, genital reconstruction,\n        repair of vascular injuries and healing of diabetic foot ulcers by vascular by-pass.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        The procedures, techniques, and principles of cosmetic surgery are entirely focused on enhancing a patientâ€™s appearance. Improving aesthetic appeal, symmetry, and proportion are the key goals. Cosmetic surgery can be performed on all areas of the head,\n        neck, and body. Because the treated areas function properly, cosmetic surgery is elective. Cosmetic surgery is practiced by doctors from a variety of medical fields, including plastic surgeons\n    </p>\n    <br>\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        The average age patients receive cosmetic surgery is 41. Treatments such as breast augmentation, liposuction, rhinoplasty (nose job) are common among younger patients\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"font15 bold\">Some of the major Plastic Surgery sub-specialties offered at our Network Hospitals in India:</p>\n\n    <ul class=\"font15\">\n        <li>Aesthetic Surgery</li>\n        <li>Reconstructive Surgery</li>\n        <li>Craniofacial Surgery</li>\n        <li>Reconstructive Microsurgery</li>\n        <li>Paediatric Plastic Surgery</li>\n        <li>Laser Surgery</li>\n        <li>Hand Surgery</li>\n        <li>Most Common Plastic Surgery procedures offered at our Network Hospitals in India</li>\n        <li>Breast</li>\n        <li>Breast Revision</li>\n        <li>Breast Lift</li>\n        <li>Breast Augmentation</li>\n        <li>Breast Reduction</li>\n        <li>Breast Implants</li>\n        <li>Male Breast Reduction</li>\n        <li>Body</li>\n        <li>Arm Lift</li>\n        <li>Post-Bariatric</li>\n        <li>Non-Surgical Fat Reduction</li>\n        <li>Tummy Tuck</li>\n        <li>Liposuction</li>\n        <li>Body Contouring</li>\n        <li>Lower Body Lift</li>\n        <li>Aesthetic Genital surgery</li>\n        <li>Pubic fat liposuction</li>\n        <li>Pubic lift</li>\n        <li>Vaginal tightening (VAGINOPLASTY)</li>\n        <li>Head</li>\n        <li>Nose Reshaping</li>\n        <li>Facelift</li>\n        <li>Cheek Augmentation</li>\n        <li>Facial Implants</li>\n        <li>Chin Augmentation</li>\n        <li>Forehead Lift</li>\n        <li>Ear Surgery</li>\n        <li>Hair Transplantation</li>\n        <li>Eyelid Surgery</li>\n        <li>Lip Augmentation</li>\n        <li>Skin</li>\n        <li>Chemical Peel Deep</li>\n        <li>Laser Hair Removal</li>\n        <li>Non-surgical skin tightening</li>\n        <li>Micro-pigmentation</li>\n        <li>Chemical Peel Light</li>\n        <li>Microdermabrasion</li>\n        <li>Fat Injection</li>\n        <li>Skin Resurfacing</li>\n        <li>Injectables</li>\n        <li>Spider Vein Treatment</li>\n        <li>Tattoo Removal</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <p class=\"font15\">\n        Cities where top and world renowned Cosmetic surgery hospitals and clinics situated are\n    </p>\n\n    <table class=\"table font15 table-hover\">\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Mumbai</td>\n                <td>Hyderabad</td>\n                <td>Kerala</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Delhi</td>\n                <td>Pune</td>\n                <td>Goa</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Bangalore</td>\n                <td>Nagpur</td>\n                <td>Jaipur</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Chennai</td>\n                <td>Gurgaon</td>\n                <td>Chandigarh</td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n</div>"

